{"tid":1507234,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"〔放題後遺症〕一陣將會去睇醫生，有經期異常、肚痾嘅手足可留此此post","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T08:02:37.000Z","uid":191290,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"03fa5f817cd5117788bfd3509e116f8c2800a229","tid":1507234,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"之前有啲post都提過好多手足經痛但無M嚟、經期短、流黑血、肚痾等等。今日我會去睇醫生，睇完會將個情況update上嚟畀大家參考一下，如果大家真係好辛苦就唔好再等，快啲去求醫。<br />\n<br />\n6月至今我有差唔多嘅情況，以為係壓力大，但自從8月頭黃大仙之後越嚟越嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n同大家簡述下我嘅情況：<br />\n<br />\nPeriod：<br />\n以前大約4-5日，量一般，鮮紅色。<br />\n6月得2-3日，7月1-2日，顏色較深呈暗紅。<br />\n8月已經遲咗1個星期到而家仲未嚟，谷到好辛苦，頭痛、經痛、個肚同下半身非常腫脹、脾氣勁暴躁。<br />\n<br />\n腸胃：<br />\n8月幾乎全部大便都唔係固體，一係就便秘。<br />\n去到period前嘅呢個星期差唔多日日痾4-5次，有攪肚感覺。<br />\n瞓低撳個肚，啲腸好似條條都脹卜卜咁，左下腹有時刺痛。<br />\n好多胃酸，間中想嘔，頂住頂住咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外精神亦都好差，有呼吸唔暢順等等嘅情況，身體差咗好多。<br />\n<br />\n各位有類似情況嘅手足可以留意呢個post，我會keep住update大家，睇完醫生之後，會講下醫生嘅意見，如果有嘅話，會share下調理身體嘅方法，希望各位手足都可以有健康身體繼續一齊打杖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e9f97ca6edc73e12fd450206c0435bf4a17d99a8","tid":1507234,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=5fac4848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"92b8d29e7f6b94a50abb2fc706269a539937db98","tid":1507234,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"為咗保障自己，我今晚返到屋企先會講自己睇咗邊個醫生，謝謝"},{"pid":"21c51aed3e8a47cc2baf0569013aeaa2491de17f","tid":1507234,"uid":180037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"保重呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccf5772748a0750ec44a37c13334e7a72f1cba0","tid":1507234,"uid":185990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:27:53.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益  對付白色恐怖嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506382\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506382</a>"},{"pid":"43c680e1c68731600610fe62133abfa6edddc7e4","tid":1507234,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"約咗大概5pm，仲有幾粒鐘，有啲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d515f213be0d617ecf088b45dbcaab8d33c728","tid":1507234,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9f97ca6edc73e12fd450206c0435bf4a17d99a8","tid":1507234,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=5fac4848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"去！！"},{"pid":"813ea8dd97f3fdc3acbbabfe9bfbced7e88c3946","tid":1507234,"uid":31974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"各絲打手